OL,3,CMillions to be spent on filling in
OL,4,Cpotholes
OL,6,FMotorist misery could soon be eased as
OL,7,Fa pothole blitz is about to get
OL,8,Funderway in Kent.
OL,10,FThe County Council is preparing to
OL,11,Fplough millions in extra cash into
OL,12,Ftackling road defects. Additional
OL,13,Ffunding from the Department for
OL,14,FTransport (DfT) worth #8.6 million
OL,15,Fwill be spent between March and
OL,16,FOctober this year.
OL,18,FThe financial boost is on top of about
OL,19,F#50 million already pledged in KCC's
OL,20,Fown road and footway planned
OL,21,Fmaintenance budget.
