OL,3,CMillions to be spent on filling in
OL,4,Cpotholes
OL,6,FKent County Council (KCC) figures show
OL,7,Fthat between October and December
OL,8,F2023, there were 5,510 potholes
OL,9,Freported.
OL,11,FThis is almost twice the number
OL,12,Fcompared to the same period in 2022,
OL,13,Fwhen there were 3,073 reported
OL,14,Fpotholes.
OL,16,FThe Pothole Blitz will focus on medium
OL,17,Fto large scale resurfacing, making
OL,18,Fpermanent first-time fixes.
