OL,3,CMillions to be spent on filling in
OL,4,Cpotholes
OL,6,FSpecialist equipment, including
OL,7,Fminiature planers, pavers and diggers,
OL,8,Fwill be used to ensure the repairs can
OL,9,Fbe made with minimal disruption to the
OL,10,Ftravelling public.
OL,12,FKCC's Cabinet Member for Highways and
OL,13,FTransport, Neil Baker said, "Between
OL,14,FApril and December 2023 we repaired
OL,15,F54,814 potholes and mended or
OL,16,Fresurfaced more than 416,991m2 of
OL,17,Froad, which is equivalent to 57
OL,18,FWembley football pitches."
