OL,3,CMillions to be spent on filling in
OL,4,Cpotholes
OL,6,F"Kent's roads are among the busiest in
OL,7,Fthe country, which is why throughout
OL,8,Fthe winter we have been responding to
OL,9,Freports of potholes by completing
OL,10,Femergency repairs where defects
OL,11,Fpresent a risk to safety."
OL,13,F"With the weather improving we are
OL,14,Fturning our attention to completing
OL,15,Fpermanent fixes the first time we
OL,16,Fvisit the site, so the travelling
OL,17,Fpublic can be confident that repairs
OL,18,Fwill last."
